Description:
Build your dream now!!!
Universal Real Estate Vic proudly presents perfectly positioned Block of land occupying 294 sqm with 14 m frontage to build an ideal family home with its impressive dimensions. This beautiful parcel of land offers a fantastic opportunity to bring your dream to life and design the home of your dreams.
Located in the Cloverton Estate, community in Melbourne's north that will revolutionise residential living in Victoria. Cloverton will be a city, transforming the outer northern suburbs of Melbourne into a thriving new destination. Cloverton will become a centre of education outside of Melbourne with sought-after retail centres, well-connected public transport and medical services. Cloverton's location is further enhanced by the picturesque surrounds of the Merri Creek and 80 hectares of lush open space.
With kilometres of walking and cycle paths, hectares of sporting fields, a future Merri Creek walking trail and a massive 80 hectares of green conservation space, health and fitness will be a way of life for Cloverton residents.
With several established schools nearby and plans for another 8 schools to be built within the community over the next 30 years. State and private primary schools and high schools within easy distance of Cloverton include Aitken Creek Primary School, Hume Anglican Grammar, Craigieburn South Primary School and Mt Ridley College. Cloverton will also have a regional higher education facility in future.
The soon to be upgraded Donnybrook Train Station is just moments away from Cloverton, offering quick and easy access to the Melbourne CBD in just over half an hour. A second train station is also planned. For drivers, the major metropolitan areas can be accesses via the Hume Freeway, with a future interchange making transport even easier in the future.
Specifications:
Size: 294 sqm approx.
Frontage: 14 m
Its right time to grab the opportunity and build your Dream home. Don't miss out! Call: Gordon Garg on 0433 897 397

Perfect block for your Dream House!
This is where the dream begins! Fully-titled, this generous allotment provides the perfect place to build your brand-new home with its uniform proportions, minimal gradient & prime location in the heart of popular Cloverton Estate.

An outstanding lifestyle/investment opportunity in the north's thriving growth corridor, it also provides easy access to Donnybrook Station & the Hume Freeway.

Description:
Marvelous Opportunity In The Kallo Estate
An outstanding package of contemporary spaces and natural light, this single level home in the sought after Kallo Estate presents a simply perfect opportunity for a range of buyers.
Stainless steel appliances feature in a kitchen sitting between a formal living room and an open plan and meals and family zone that integrates seamlessly with a huge rear yard, complete with entertainers deck.
The main bedroom with its ensuite and walk in robe is zoned from the remaining three bedrooms and the family bathroom for peace and privacy, while the double garage introduces the ease and security of internal access.
Also offering side-access beside the garage, an abundance of off-street parking is available for your boat, trailer or caravan with enough room to construct an additional garage, shed of workshop in future.
With ducted heating and cooling heading a list of extra's, this won't be around for long.

Description:
Exceptional Quality & Cloverton Convenience
Beyond the established front garden & attractive facade, this beautifully-appointed home
delivers a family lifestyle of outstanding quality & versatility with its free-flowing design & extensive list of features.
Bathed in natural light, the home's inviting interior comprises a large master bedroom with fitted walk-in robe & private ensuite, two additional bedrooms (both with built-in robes), stylish main bathroom & dedicated study (potential fourth bedroom).
Adding to its family appeal is a separate lounge/TV room & fabulous open-plan living/dining
area accompanied by a sleek stone-bench kitchen complete with island/breakfast bar, walk-in
pantry & quality appliances.
Other highlights of the home include ducted heating & evaporative cooling, alarm & CCTV,
NBN connection, efficient LED lighting, plantation shutters throughout & double-glazed
windows all-round Stacker doors reveal an al-fresco entertaining area & sizeable backyard, plus a remote-control double garage with internal entry.
This premier location provides the added appeal of being close to the best of Cloverton's future masterplan amenities including the Merri Creek conservation area, a range of sports & recreational facilities, retail & dining precincts, as well as schools & the proposed Cloverton Station, plus easy access now to both Donnybrook Station & the Hume Freeway.
